for items in hunt</span><hr size=1> Xakra Kel armor from Shadeweaver's Thicket is No Rent (and shouldn't be No Drop here). Ditto for Whiptail Scorpion Glands from Shar Vahl. Actually, a heck of alot of things from Luclin (quest-related) are No Rent and would be ideal for a scavenger hunt.<br>
<br>
Another idea would be to get oddball items for quests that are not particularly popular, so folks aren't likely to have them on-hand. For example, the Kobold Missionary (level 25 or so) in Steamfont drops An Encrypted Document which is one of the final items needed for the Quellious Regent quest for Erudite Clerics. I can't say I have ever seen anyone actually visiting us gnomes for that quest.<br>
<br>
I am sure there are a bunch of other underutilized quests out there... I keep hearing there are almost no human Bertoxxulous worshippers on this server, so maybe some of their quest bits? Or maybe some of the older quests that don't get done much anymore, since new and improved quests were added?<br>
